Name: AccountId
EnhancedDefinition: A unique and immutable identifier used to identify the account resource. This identifier has no meaning to the account owner.

Name: ProductIdentifier
EnhancedDefinition: Identifier within the parent organisation for the product. Must be unique in the organisation.

Name: ProductType
EnhancedDefinition: Descriptive code for the product category.

Name: ProductName
EnhancedDefinition: The name of the product used for marketing purposes from a customer perspective. I.e. what the customer would recognise.

Name: SecondaryProductIdentifier
EnhancedDefinition: Identifier within the parent organisation for the product. Must be unique in the organisation.
